<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I have read the whole trilogy and I think that each book can be read as a stand alone.<br/>In any order.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I have read the whole trilogy and I think that each book can be read as a stand alone.<br />In any order.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
