    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3492426015" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3492426015" />
    <a title="Henry" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/63028700-henry"><img alt="Henry" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1562101030p2/63028700.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3492426015?book_show_action=true">Aug 21, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Henry" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Henry" href="/user/show/63028700-henry">Henry</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/33245905-the-magnificent-ambersons">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3492426015" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9470818435991699604">Magnificent novel but you have to get past the totally despicable and unlikable main character, George Amberson Minafer, and the dysfunctional and unhealthy (not sexually but psychological) relationship with his mother. If you can this is a beautifully written and engrossing novel of late nineteenth, early twentieth century America with an addictive plot. Well worthy of the 1919 Pulitzer Prize.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3492426015">
